title: SubDownloader v.2.0.7.0-Full-multilanguage by BabyBoy.rar
description:

Some of you might already know this software.
So, the latest version at this moment it's not for free (30 days evaluation#, even if it was free the last year. I can say that i cracked the latest release and at the same time i can say i did not...Why ?
I took the 2.0.9.3 version #Run.exe#(latest at the moment on the official site) and install it on my PC. After that i took the executable #Run.exe) from the 2.0.7.0 version (the latest FREE version - which i haded copied long time ago when i had it installed on my PC) and substitute the executable (Run.exe)2.0.9.3. in the directory where is installed. After all of this i launched the application and it worked...
